				</listitem>
				<listitem>
					<para>fedora  - a required parameter specifying the Fedora servlet path. </para>
				</listitem>
				<listitem>
					<para>get - a required parameter specifying the Fedora servlet path </para>
				</listitem>
				<listitem>
					<para>PID – PID of the object for which you wish to retrieve its object profile. </para>
				</listitem>
				<listitem>
					<para>fedora-system:3 – PID of the behavior definition object for the default disseminator. </para>
				</listitem>
				<listitem>
					<para>getObjectProfile – method name to retrieve an object’s profile in XML format. </para>
